snippet.title: Holiday Party: Mascot Brawl Trailer 2
snippet.description:
Holiday Party: Mascot Brawl is a fast-paced multiplayer Party Game with quirky holiday mascot characters. Engage in battles with a variety of unique weapons and simple combo attacks.

Please follow us on the Steam page and Discord community:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2282650/Holiday_Party/
https://discord.gg/K7V5sSGz
